I am not a big fan of this convention. It is overly complicated and puts responder in complete charge of the auction. And there are some hands where opener would like a more cooperative auction with both partners participating. I have seen many examples where pairs who use this convention get to a bad contract when using standard bidding would have gotten them to the correct contract. So I have pretty strong feelings that you should not play this (although you may run into some good players who disagree with me).|
